metadata.name: RALIAH; the girl with  the sauce
metadata.description:
What can I say about life?  
Life can be hard,  
Life can be dangerous,  
Life can be scary,  
Life can be none of these,  
Life can be amazing,  
Life can be sweet,  
Life can be enjoyed,  
Life can make you a sugar girl,  
Life can be what we choose to be,  
Life can be pink and beautiful,  
Life can be the girl with the sauce.
